    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Symphony of the Stars is a JRPG that sees a lost outsider, Myst, thrown into a war between the gods of the zodiac! Explore and battle your way through puzzle box dungeons as you seek out powerful relics that grant the use of both combat and overworld skills. Delve into themes of duality and personal growth with Myst as he weighs the preservation of his past against the embrace of an uncertain future. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Original soundtrack inspired by the SNES era</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Overworld skills that enhance exploration, change how you interact with enemies, and open up new areas</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lore, treasure, and secrets can be found in every corner of this large fantasy world</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A variety of biomes and puzzles wait to be explored and solved across 13 unique dungeons</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Battle mechanics in which skills and primary attacks work together to deal maximum damage</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187490/extras/9f2ec1bcd3f2a4a41a82aa64d3e8ac1e.avif?t=1769438339\" width=560 height=80 /></span><strong>Customize your characters in battle by learning and equipping devastating skills!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187490/extras/3275482e29d6480397f3082f9b9f9b9c.poster.avif?t=1769438339\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187490/extras/3275482e29d6480397f3082f9b9f9b9c.webm?t=1769438339\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187490/extras/3275482e29d6480397f3082f9b9f9b9c.mp4?t=1769438339\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187490/extras/ce674637509a370fd528b1f50cf851a4.avif?t=1769438339\" width=560 height=80 /></span><strong>Use skills to interact with the world outside of battle!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187490/extras/524e7930cfd2aabf9fa7dbd7bf45894f.poster.avif?t=1769438339\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187490/extras/524e7930cfd2aabf9fa7dbd7bf45894f.webm?t=1769438339\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187490/extras/524e7930cfd2aabf9fa7dbd7bf45894f.mp4?t=1769438339\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187490/extras/15af2aa24dd925c24ff96e6187733dfd.avif?t=1769438339\" width=560 height=80 /></span><strong>Solve a variety of puzzles to earn items, upgrade characters, and complete dungeons!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187490/extras/f5e23c77ebef8d950c3163d7080480d4.poster.avif?t=1769438339\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https: